{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/gate_3.gif?t=1563852035\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to the Lost Castle. R U READY for some challenge?</h2><br><br>Guided by an old treasure map, Jess is now standing in front of a castle. With all these ruins around, the castle seems to be abandoned for a long time.<br><br>A light glittering at the top of the castle, exuding a feeling of mysterious... Jess knows, this won't be an easy adventure.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/torch_2.gif?t=1563852035\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAMEPLAY</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Search every inch of the castle, discover the secret of it, gather all the item it needs to finish the game;<br></li><li>Some monsters have entrenched themselves in the deep of the castle, defeat them to make your way into the central of castle;<br></li><li>Find out the chests laying in the corner of castle, notice all the hints that were given.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/boss3_appear.gif?t=1563852035\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Well-designed game map, shortcuts inspiring players to discover &amp; gather;<br></li><li>Light, physical, movement, jigsaw, maze, number...all kinds of puzzle waiting for your challenge;<br></li><li>Use different functions of your weapon to defeat enemies or get through special obstacles.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/run_6.gif?t=1563852035\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Sound of the devs</h2><br><br>Hi everyone, it is a pleasure to bring you our first game <i>Dawn of the Lost Castle</i><br><br>As a big fan of <i>Castlevania</i>, I wanted the game to contains more exploration elements and more fights. But it didn't go well since we all lack of experiences and funds to extend the development period.  <br><br>But this won't be the end of <i>Dawn of the Lost Castle</i>, neither it will be our last game. So if you have any suggestions, please let us know through Steam Discussion.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/sun_1.gif?t=1563852035\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Super Player","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1018170/b0a3d8579f75c21dbc31660ee8549d738e848b86.jpg"},{"name":"Senior Player","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1018170/4c6ee6c444aa7cc8719e999fe567596d344a0b7c.jpg"},{"name":"Historical_Digger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1018170/99c13ac34f00fd966a8605dcdf1343cae96c4330.jpg"},{"name":"Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1018170/8a99fe91b338f706494478d5882fd6f18025a25f.jpg"},{"name":"Rogues","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1018170/285a109b838e861e1d95a7afe987bc40b181340c.jpg"},{"name":"Night hermit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1018170/7f146ecee58a3991c4041fe0d504127855dbe7c7.jpg"}],"total":6},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1563852035","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/page.bg.jpg?t=1563852035","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1563852035","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1563852035","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"